Includes also original autograph letters by Marcello Malpighi (6 items) and Gaetano Atti (3
        items); manuscript Tractatus in libros de generatione (17th century), on reproduction,
        sensation, and the theory of knowledge; typescript bibliography of the works of Fabricius;
        typescript with pencilled notes on manuscripts by Malpighi; and glass slides including
        portraits of Malpighi. Libraries where unbound photocopies were made are not identified;
        wood blocks and their origin are also unidentified.
